<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{pageTitle}}</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">{{pageTitle}}</h1>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <h3>중첩 객체 접근 예제</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4>문법 설명</h4>
            <p class="text-muted">객체 안의 객체 속성에 점(.) 표기법으로 접근합니다. (예: {{user.address.city}}</p>

            <h4>사용자 정보 (중첩 객체)</h4>
            {{#user}}
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">{{name}}님의 프로필</h5>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <h6>기본 정보</h6>
                                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                    <li><strong>이름:</strong>{{name}}</li>
                                    <li><strong>이메일:</strong>{{email}}</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <h6>주소 정보(중첩 객체)</h6>
                                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                    <li><strong>도시:</strong>{{address.city}}</li>
                                    <li><strong>상세 주소:</strong>{{address.street}}</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {{/user}}

            <h4>중첩 객체 섹션 사용</h4>
            <div class="alert alert-primary">
                {{#user}}
                    {{#address}}
                        <p><strong>주소 정보가 있습니다:</strong></p>
                        <p>{{city}}시 {{street}}에 거주하고 계시네요!</p>
                    {{/address}}
                {{/user}}
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4">

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <a href="/mustache/partials" class="btn btn-secondary">이전</a>
        <a href="/mustache/complex-data" class="btn btn-primary">다음: 복합 데이터 학습</a>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>